Mexico to Disclose Oil Hedge Data After 2012 Budget Approval

-- B y   A d r i a n a   L o p e z   C a r a v e o
-- 
2011-10-06T17:00:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-06/mexico-to-disclose-oil-hedge-data-after-2012-budget-approval.html
Mexico ’s government will disclose
details about oil hedges for next year’s production after the
2012 budget has been approved in Congress, said Jose Antonio
Gonzalez Anaya, deputy minister of income at the  Finance
Ministry .  He spoke in Mexico City today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
